Program: Omnibus
Title: Children of the Nazis
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jhb
Last Broadcast Date: 29 April 1988
"Hitler was a good man". Speaking to children whose parents were committed members of the Nazi party and supporters of Hitler. Includes interviews with the daughter of Martin Bormann, Niklas Frank, son of Hans Frank and the son of Wolfram Sievers, who conducted experiments on humans.